1
0:00:00.000 --> 0:00:17.000
They say they love each other, I know that they do.
他们说他们相爱，我知道他们是真心的。

2
0:00:17.000 --> 0:00:25.000
They say they'll always be together, that may not be true.
他们说他们会永远在一起，但也许不是真的。

3
0:00:25.000 --> 0:00:32.000
They come from different places, different points of view.
他们来自不同的地方，有不同的观点。

4
0:00:32.000 --> 0:00:40.000
They find themselves in different spaces, everything is all brand new.
他们发现自己在不同的空间，一切都是全新的。

5
0:00:40.000 --> 0:00:47.000
Two different directions, too many different ways.
两种不同的方向，太多不同的方式。

6
0:00:47.000 --> 0:00:55.000
One always on the road somewhere, the other one always stays.
一个总是在路上，另一个总是待在原地。

7
0:00:55.000 --> 0:01:02.000
Too often unhappy, too often on your own.
太常不开心，太常独自一人。

8
0:01:02.000 --> 0:01:10.000
When you are moving in different directions, true love is all alone.
当你们朝不同的方向前进，真爱就孤独了。

9
0:01:10.000 --> 0:01:17.000
Old stories start to surface, patterns from long ago.
旧故事开始浮出水面，来自很久以前的模式。

10
0:01:17.000 --> 0:01:25.000
And loving quickly turns to anger, for reasons they don't even know.
而且爱很快变成了愤怒，原因他们甚至不知道。

11
0:01:25.000 --> 0:01:32.000
The strongest heart can be broken with one insensitive word.
最坚强的心也会因一句无情的话而破碎。

12
0:01:32.000 --> 0:01:41.000
The deepest feelings remain unspoken, no one is seen, nothing heard.
最深的感情未曾言说，无人可见，没有声音传出。

13
0:01:41.000 --> 0:01:48.000
Two different directions, too many different ways.
两种不同的方向，太多不同的方式。

14
0:01:48.000 --> 0:01:56.000
One always wants to work things out, the other one wants to play.
一个总是想解决问题，另一个想玩。

15
0:01:56.000 --> 0:02:03.000
Too ready for changes, and too much that just can't wait.
太容易改变，太多事情不能等待。

16
0:02:03.000 --> 0:02:11.000
When you are moving in different directions, true love can turn to hate.
当你们朝不同的方向前进，真爱可以变成憎恨。

17
0:02:11.000 --> 0:02:19.000
If opposites attract each other, what's the reason for?
如果相反的东西相互吸引，原因是什么？

18
0:02:19.000 --> 0:02:28.000
One being like an open window, one just like a closing door.
一个像敞开的窗户，一个就像关闭的门。

19
0:02:28.000 --> 0:02:35.000
Two different directions, too many different ways.
两种不同的方向，太多不同的方式。

20
0:02:35.000 --> 0:02:43.000
One likes to see the morning sunrise, the other one sleeps in bed.
一个喜欢看早晨的日出，另一个睡在床上。

21
0:02:43.000 --> 0:02:50.000
Too many tomorrow, too many times too late.
明天太多，太多次都太迟了。

22
0:02:50.000 --> 0:02:58.000
When you are moving in different directions, true love may have to wait.
当你们朝不同的方向前进，真爱也许必须等待。

23
0:02:58.000 --> 0:03:07.000
If you are committed to different directions, true love will have to wait.
如果你们朝不同的方向承诺，真爱将不得不等待。

24
0:03:13.000 --> 0:03:19.000
Thank you for watching!
谢谢观看！
